description: TWO GARAGE PARKING! Must see expansive corner 2 bedroom 2 bathroom in well run HOA. Featuring 1,200 sq.ft. of luxury living with every amenity, this unit features an open floor-plan with a renovated kitchen showcasing a subzero refrigerator, new stove & dishwasher plus tons of counter & cabinet space. Separate dinning area. Entertaining size living room with gas fireplace. Gleaming hardwood floors with cherry inlay. Washer/Dryer in-unit. Huge foyer with built-ins, pantry storage, & wine fridge. Two equal size bedrooms including main bedroom with ensuite bath. Views of Boston skyline from the unit and amazing roof deck! Unit upgrades include brand new HVAC in 2023, New Stove & wine fridge in 2022. Building upgrades include new roof in 2024 and New foyer/entry door in 2024. Elevator building!
